Part I. Reading Notes 阅读笔记
	1. Decaf Language Reference Manual
	Decaf language的词法和语法规范以sunysb-decaf版本为准，Brown和TAMU版本的文档作为参考。
	
	2. ANTLR v3 快速入门教程
	Read TDAR(The Definitive ANTLR Reference) Chpt.1 Section 1.3~1.5, Chpt.3 Section 3.1
	其他参考资料:
	http://www.antlr.org/wiki/display/ANTLR3/FAQ+-+Getting+Started
	http://www.antlr.org/wiki/display/ANTLR3/Five+minute+introduction+to+ANTLR+3
		
	3. Quick Review of Regular Expression, NFA, and DFA
	Read Engineering A Compiler, 2ed Chpt.2 Section 2.1~2.4
	其他参考资料:
	CS373@UIUC lecture slides & videos:
	http://www.cs.uiuc.edu/class/sp10/cs373/lectures/index.html
	
	4. (Optional)Implemeting Regular Expressions by Russ Cox
	关于Coding实现正则表达式的一系列精彩文章:
	http://swtch.com/~rsc/regexp/
	
	5. (Optional)Hand-coding Lexer(手写词法分析器)
	Read Engineering A Compiler, 2ed Chpt.2 Section 2.5
	
	相关Project:
	cs164fa04@berkeley PA2:
	http://www-inst.eecs.berkeley.edu/~cs164/fa04/Assignments/pa2.pdf
	
	6. LL-based Grammar Analysis
	
	
	7. LL-based Lexer vs. DFA-based Lexer &
	   ANTLR vs. Lex, Flex
	
	
	8. ANTLR v3's Predicated-LL(*) Lexer	
	Read "ANTLR lexer in depth":
	https://wincent.com/wiki/ANTLR_lexers_in_depth


